mixin CustomizeBlock(config)
  h5= config.title
  p.my-2 To change the #{config.title.toLowerCase()} of the Navbar Vertical , update the SCSS variable 
    code= config.scssVar
    |  in your 
    code _user-variables.scss 
    | or CSS variable 
    code= config.cssVar
    |  in your 
    code public/assets/css/user.css. 
    | Example:
  +ComponentCardLib('css').mb-4.
    //- _user-variables.scss
    #{config.scssVar}: #{config.egValue};
    or,
    //- public/assets/css/user.css
    #{config.cssVar}: #{config.egValue};